Package: packTemplate
Type: Package
Title: A template used as a basis for developing R packages to my liking
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
	person("Alex", "Baker", email = "alexbakercreates@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-2844-9720"))
Description: Building an R package has an element of choice and style and I have bundled these into a template.
    This package provided a templated package set-up for my own used which covers:
        Testing
        Automatic documentation using roxygen2
        pre-commit code formatting and cleaning
        Building and including vignettes
        A package website that should work on github pages
        A package logo
